  "keyFeatures": [
    "22 production-ready React components for documentation sites",
    "Tailwind CSS v3 and v4 support with themeable design tokens",
    "Syntax-highlighted code blocks powered by Shiki",
    "Mermaid diagram rendering with pan/zoom controls",
    "Accessible keyboard navigation (ARIA tree, tabs, accordion)",
    "Dark mode support out of the box",
    "Search modal with recent searches and keyboard shortcuts",
    "Compound component patterns (Accordion.Group, Tabs.Item, Steps.Item, Color.Row/Item, Tree.File/Folder)"
